{"title":"微信小程序-WXSS的书写格式","date":"2023-04-06T14:06:34.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Apr 6, 2023","L":"04/06/2023","MM-DD":"04-06"},"link":"2023/04/06/Web/微信小程序/wxss/14-微信小程序-WXSS的书写格式","tags":["微信小程序"],"updated":"2023-04-06T14:36:42.690Z","content":"<h1 id=\"行内样式\">行内样式<a title=\"#行内样式\" href=\"#行内样式\"></a></h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;color: red;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>行内样式<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"页面样式\">页面样式<a title=\"#页面样式\" href=\"#页面样式\"></a></h1>\n<p>编写在当前页面文件夹当中的 WXML 的 WXSS 文件当中：</p>\n<p>index.wxss:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.pageStyle</span> &#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: pink;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;pageStyle&quot;</span>&gt;</span>页面样式<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"全局样式\">全局样式<a title=\"#全局样式\" href=\"#全局样式\"></a></h1>\n<p>编写在 app.wxss 文件当中：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-class\">.globalStyle</span> &#123;<br>  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#f0f</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>index.wxml:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;globalStyle&quot;</span>&gt;</span>全局样式<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"优先级\">优先级<a title=\"#优先级\" href=\"#优先级\"></a></h1>\n<p>分别为：行内样式 &gt; 页面样式 &gt; 全局样式，如果想让其中的某一个样式达到最高可以利用之前 CSS 所学习的 <code>!important</code> 来实现。</p>\n<p>行内样式 &gt; 页面样式 &gt; 全局样式：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;color: red;&quot;</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;pageStyle globalStyle&quot;</span>&gt;</span>行内样式<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>页面样式 &gt; 全局样式:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs html\"><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">class</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;pageStyle globalStyle&quot;</span>&gt;</span>页面样式<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">view</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>!important:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><code class=\"hljs plaintext\">.globalStyle &#123;<br>  color: #f0f !important;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img2023.cnblogs.com/blog/2105804/202304/2105804-20230406223638243-240821008.png\" alt=\"image-20230406223637186\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"微信小程序-新增RPX响应式单位","link":"2023/04/06/Web/微信小程序/wxss/15-微信小程序-新增RPX响应式单位"},"next":{"title":"微信小程序-WXSS学什么","link":"2023/04/06/Web/微信小程序/wxss/13-微信小程序-WXSS学什么"},"plink":"http://example.com/2023/04/06/Web/微信小程序/wxss/14-微信小程序-WXSS的书写格式/","toc":[{"id":"行内样式","title":"行内样式","index":"1"},{"id":"页面样式","title":"页面样式","index":"2"},{"id":"全局样式","title":"全局样式","index":"3"},{"id":"优先级","title":"优先级","index":"4"}],"reading_time":"200 words in 1 min"}